          CONCEPTS:
            Full model is <count><verb><count><motion>
              <count><motion>       # navigation 20j
              <verb><count><motion> # editing    d20j
              <count><verb><motion> # editing    20gUj
                  
            lowercase/UPPERCASE versions do it BIGGER or OPPOSITE

            <shift>: opens a "command palette" mode

          PLUGIN, CONFIG, & TOOL MANAGEMENT:
            <leader>l     open p[l]ugin manager
            <leader>fc    [f]ind [p]config files
            <leader>sk    show all key mappings
            :LazyExtras   open Lazy Extras mode

          EDITING:
            .             Use to repeat any change

            {count}J      (j)oin line(s) with the line below
            I             INSERT mode at beginning of line
            A             INSERT mode at end of line
            gu{motion}    lowercase over a motion
            guu           lowercase a full line
            {count}gcc    comment line
            66i*<Escape>  Makes a ruler, cool!
            ciw           Deletes the inner word and enters Insert Mode
            C             d$ and enter Insert Mode

          NAVIGATION:
            <Space>fm     Mini.files plugin
            s<pattern>    (s)eek visible pattern in open windows
            <C-o>         go (o)ut to last place
            <C-i>         go (i)n to next place
            [m            jump to start of previous function
            ]m            jump to start of next function

          COOLNESS:
            gx            Open a link under your cursor in the browser
            gww           Format the text width!



